<title type="html"><![CDATA[8/17(Sat.)Stress at work is 'causing' poor mental health in men/ Eat more plants to live longer( Host:William and Danny)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=308&amp;p=324#p324"><![CDATA[
8/17(Sat.) Stress at work is 'causing' poor mental health in men/ Eat more plants and less meat to live longer and improve heart health, study suggests( Host: William and Danny)<br /><br /><br />Article 1:Stress at work is 'causing' poor mental health in men<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/40875128/stress-at-work-is-causing-poor-mental-health-in-men">http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/4 ... lth-in-men</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. Do you feel stressful at work?<br />2. How do you relieve the stress?<br />3. In terms of your work, can you took time off due to mental health?<br />4. Please share some story about your stress at work.(or at home)<br /><br /><br />Article 2:Eat more plants and less meat to live longer and improve heart health, study suggests<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://edition.cnn.com/2019/08/09/health/plant-based-diet-heart-disease-study/index.html">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/08/09/heal ... index.html</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Discussion<br />1. Are you or your relative a vegetarian? Why or why not (The reason you insist in eating meat or not.)<br />2. What do you think after reading this article? Can you have a meal without meat?(vegetarian definitely yes, you can skip the question)<br />3. Can you share your tips to keep health? Or share what you eat today and tell us the reason.<br /><br />Agenda<br />7:00 ~ 7:30 pm greetings &amp; free talk <br />7:30 ~ 8:15 pm guests introduced &amp; first session discussion <br />8:15 ~ 8:45 pm presentation, sharing the article &amp; other experiences <br />8:45 ~ 9:30 pm second session discussion<br /><br />Position: Dante coffee Shop (丹堤咖啡), MRT板南線 - 新埔站2號出口, next to 7-Seven, <br />板橋民生路二段237 號, <br />Time: PM 7:00-9:30, <br />a minimum charge of Dante coffee for Royal English club attendant NT$80 (丹提低消80元)<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500.請帶著開放與熱情來學英文<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Mon Aug 12, 2019 12:20 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
